{"id": 1238, "genre": 1001, "title": "你无法忍受什么样的怀旧？", "description": "怀旧什么时候也成了一种从众行为？（题图来自：Mario Zucca）", "record_count": 3890, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201609231436263w7UmIO4xVXAy0aJ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-24T17:00:33Z", "options": [{"id": 119296, "content": "用瓷缸子喝水 就是觉得脏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658168}, {"id": 119297, "content": "拍很多烂片，冠以怀旧之名。引得一大堆人蜂拥而至", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743142}, {"id": 119299, "content": "用以前和现在做对比，比来比去还是你自己?", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649741}, {"id": 119300, "content": "一直回忆在过去，束缚自己前进的脚步！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766241}, {"id": 119303, "content": "恶心的滤镜", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 32419}, {"id": 120327, "content": "前女友?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776288}, {"id": 120328, "content": "顶多怀念小时候单纯开心快乐的日子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776813}, {"id": 120584, "content": "青春烂片", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 765146}, {"id": 121352, "content": "吹牛逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 780433}, {"id": 119310, "content": "总是回忆过去   过去，偶尔拿出来回忆一下就可以  如果总是回忆过去  说明你现在过得并不怎么样  而且还是一个不善于改变现状的人。", "image": "img/option/option/20160925170932qCs4Nmx5pSno2hDU.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736404}, {"id": 120078, "content": "那些讲着怀旧的电影却一点也不怀旧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645950}, {"id": 119311, "content": "小店们搞成一副怀旧的样子。进入就当旅游吧，但不会买。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1030252}, {"id": 119312, "content": "没创新接受不了新事物而刻意的怀旧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 756518}, {"id": 119569, "content": "洒狗血般的石更煽情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773570}, {"id": 119314, "content": "陷在过去死活不面对现实", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766293}, {"id": 119315, "content": "把怀旧肤浅的定义为：早恋，逃学，怀孕堕胎，与全世界为敌", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772037}, {"id": 119316, "content": "青春篇里", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760323}, {"id": 119319, "content": "怀旧 是因为不想面对现实", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772070}, {"id": 124440, "content": "不晓得", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796278}, {"id": 119322, "content": "怀旧只是因为现在过得不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766813}, {"id": 119324, "content": "想吃辣条，五毛钱一袋的那种！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744039}, {"id": 119326, "content": "用怀旧来让自己看上去有阅历", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772113}, {"id": 152352, "content": "我也算是半个老玩家了，balala经过的版本多少个我的职业从来都没有改成这样过。不玩你滚啊。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597341}, {"id": 119328, "content": "洒下太多鸡汤和狗血的青春怀旧，青春为什么一定是旧呢？像微微一笑就很好，甜的让人想微笑?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 771595}, {"id": 119329, "content": "越老越怀旧，只是自己不再有的青葱岁月！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772126}, {"id": 152355, "content": "商业化", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898058}, {"id": 119331, "content": "不明不白的那一段岁月！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772128}, {"id": 119338, "content": "我不喜欢 我本来就不喜欢的人怀旧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436982}, {"id": 130858, "content": "不是非得要堕胎吸毒的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797189}, {"id": 121389, "content": "青春片感觉有点假  和大部分人的都不一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 757239}, {"id": 124205, "content": "嗯⋯⋯⋯怎麼說呢？就好像中國的青春爛片吧⋯⋯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 795616}, {"id": 119342, "content": "与物喻物", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772112}, {"id": 119598, "content": "时隔几十年让经典电视剧电影的扮演者再已以前的扮相出镜，真毁童年。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773681}, {"id": 119343, "content": "不装", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 624114}, {"id": 121903, "content": "类似于45度角仰望天空，眼角有翔划过这样的怀旧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766851}, {"id": 119345, "content": "“那是我逝去的青春”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772159}, {"id": 118578, "content": "看到讲五月天的文章就分享到朋友圈，不管有多久没听过他们的歌了", "image": null, "praise_count": 85, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 118579, "content": "各种同学聚会之后必发合影到朋友圈，配上煽情句子", "image": null, "praise_count": 417, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 118580, "content": "天天讲自己想回到校园时光，其实只是因为那个时候翘课不扣钱，现在翘班扣钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 273, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 118581, "content": "见到咪咪虾条之类“小时候的零食”就很激动地去买，然后并不会吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 115, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 119350, "content": "宿舍夜谈时突然讲起小时候看过的动画片……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118276}, {"id": 118584, "content": "所有照片都加上令人抑郁的暗黄调滤镜", "image": null, "praise_count": 227, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 119352, "content": "怀旧还是挺美的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770905}, {"id": 119353, "content": "商业目的性很强的各种活动。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651564}, {"id": 122425, "content": "打着怀旧，情怀牌，不进反退，抄袭有理", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 483495}, {"id": 119354, "content": "所谓的情怀和怀旧电影", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224827}, {"id": 119357, "content": "无法忍受回忆青春之类的电影电视", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 754626}, {"id": 120384, "content": "不能忍受打着怀旧旗帜的手机游戏，无耻的圈钱！\n不能忍受旧时喜欢的动漫无脑复制翻拍！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776954}, {"id": 119365, "content": "用怀旧的手段换眼泪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772320}, {"id": 119366, "content": "一反驳就会听到你们懂什么，我在怀旧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714145}]}